Cool product! This is fairly unrelated but since you&#x27;ve open-sourced your code (thanks!) I was just browsing around the &#x27;cli&#x27; project and saw heaps of the following:<p><pre><code>  if err != nil {
      stdcli.Error(err)
      return
  }
</code></pre>
Is this idiomatic Go? It&#x27;s just sprinkled everywhere and makes it hard to follow logic at a glance.
